concept.title: Comparison

conbody.p: Below are the comparison between Katalon Recorder and Selenium IDE:

li.p: KR: users are able to start recording tests on the current tab immediately
S.IDE: users must create/open a project, specify a URL and then start recording
KR: supports test suites and test cases
S.IDE: There is a little bit hard to manage test suites/test cases
KR: Drag and drop to arrange test suites, test cases, and test steps
S.IDE: Drag and drop to arrange test steps

row.entry: KR enables dashboard view with TestOps
KR supports CSV, JSON as data sources
KR allows developers to add custom locators and actions
